snippet.title: Seashell Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Relax, make time for yourself, and collect unique and beautiful gifts from the sea in Seashell. "Learn about the creatures who lived inside the seashells in descriptions written by marine biologist Dr. Helen Scales. Gain research level badges and become a Friend of the Sea." https://store.steampowered.com/app/1829540/Seashell/ #indiegames #marinebiology #seashells
